#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.pie.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.pie"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:1
#: of
msgid "Generate a pie plot."
msgstr "生成一个饼图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:3
#: of
msgid ""
"A pie plot is a proportional representation of the numerical data in a "
"column. This function wraps :meth:`matplotlib.pyplot.pie` for the "
"specified column. If no column reference is passed and ``subplots=True`` "
"a pie plot is drawn for each numerical column independently."
msgstr ""
"饼图是某一列中数值数据的比例表示。此函数对指定列包装了 :meth:`matplotlib."
"pyplot.pie`。如果未传递列引用且 ``subplots=True``，则会为每个数值列独立"
"绘制饼图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:9
#: of
msgid ""
"Label or position of the column to plot. If not provided, "
"``subplots=True`` argument must be passed."
msgstr "要绘制的列的标签或位置。如果未提供，则必须传递 ``subplots=True`` 参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:12
#: of
msgid "Keyword arguments to pass on to :meth:`DataFrame.plot`."
msgstr "传递给 :meth:`DataFrame.plot` 的关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:14
#: of
msgid "A NumPy array is returned when `subplots` is True."
msgstr "当 `subplots` 为 True 时返回一个 NumPy 数组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:19
#: of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.plot.pie`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:20
#: of
msgid "Generate a pie plot for a Series."
msgstr "为 Series 生成一个饼图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:22
#: of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.plot`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:23
#: of
msgid "Make plots of a DataFrame."
msgstr "绘制 DataFrame 的图表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:26
#: of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:27
#: of
msgid ""
"In the example below we have a DataFrame with the information about "
"planet's mass and radius. We pass the 'mass' column to the pie function "
"to get a pie plot."
msgstr ""
"在下面的示例中，我们有一个包含行星质量和半径信息的 DataFrame。我们将 '"
"mass' 列传递给饼图函数以获得饼图。"

